         MACRO
&NAME    RLCOMM &MODE
         LCLC  &GNAME
&GNAME   SETC  '@Q@'.'&SYSNDX'
.*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
.* RLCOMM  - Common DSECT for RMTLOG components.
.* RLCOMM CONST - Define common constants.
.* RLCOMM DSECT - Define common DSECT.
.*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
.*
